'''安德雷·祖博夫'''（{{lang-ru|'''Андрей Борисович Зубов'''}}，拉丁转写：{{lang|en|'''Andrei Borisovich Zubov'''}}，{{bd|1952年|1月16日|catIdx=Zubov}}），全名'''安德雷·博里索维奇·祖博夫'''，[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[历史学家|历史学家]]、[[政治学家|政治学家]]，历史学博士。祖博夫1973年毕业于[[莫斯科國立國際關係學院|莫斯科國立國際關係學院]]，后来在莫斯科國立國際關係學院任教授。2014年3月，祖博夫发表文章，将俄罗斯吞并[[克里米亚|克里米亚]]与[[纳粹德国|纳粹德国]]吞并[[奥地利|奥地利]]相提并论，他随即因此被莫斯科國立國際關係學院解职。<ref name="res">{{Cite news |last = Bodner |first = Matthew |date = 5 March 2014 |title = Professor says sacked over opinion article |url = http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/professor-says-sacked-over-opinion-article-against-possible-ukraine-invasion/495616.html |work = [[The_Moscow_Times|themoscowtimes.com]] |accessdate = 25 March 2014 |archive-date = 2016-06-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160605030930/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/professor-says-sacked-over-opinion-article-against-possible-ukraine-invasion/495616.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = "Bloom fire">{{Cite news |last = Bershidsky |first = Leonid |date = 25 March 2014 |title = Comparing Putin to Hitler Will Get You Fired |url = http://www.bloombergview.com/articles/2014-03-25/comparing-putin-to-hitler-will-get-you-fired |work = [[bloomberg.com|bloomberg.com]] |accessdate = 25 March 2014 |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075031/http://www.bloombergview.com/articles/2014-03-25/comparing-putin-to-hitler-will-get-you-fired |dead-url = no }}</ref>

